# NOTICE

This project implements an experimental Format Preserving Encryption FF3 algorithm as specified in NIST SP 800-38G.

## References and Attribution

### NIST Specification
- **NIST Special Publication 800-38G** - Recommendation for Block Cipher Modes of Operation: Methods for Format-Preserving Encryption
- **Authors**: Morris Dworkin
- **Published**: March 2016
- **Source**: https://doi.org/10.6028/NIST.SP.800-38G

### Implementation References
- **Clean-room implementation** - Built directly from NIST SP 800-38G specification
- **Academic Papers**: Cryptanalysis and security research papers on FF3-1
- **FIPS 197**: Advanced Encryption Standard (AES) specification
- **Educational resources**: Format-preserving encryption implementation studies

### Test Framework
- Algorithm validation based on NIST SP 800-38G patterns
- Educational test cases for algorithm study

## Cryptographic Acknowledgments

FF3-1 algorithm specified by NIST based on academic research in format-preserving encryption.

